---
import Layout from '../../components/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Technical SEO Optimization for Astro Sites - Rank Higher on Google"
  description="Expert technical SEO optimization for Astro websites. Improve Core Web Vitals, structured data, and search rankings with performance-first SEO."
  keywords="technical SEO, Astro SEO optimization, Core Web Vitals, structured data, search engine optimization, SEO audit">
  
  <section class="service-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <h1 class="hero-title">SEO That Actually <em>Ranks</em></h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle">
          Technical SEO optimization that leverages Astro's performance advantages to dominate search results. 
          We don't just optimize‚Äîwe engineer for rankings.
        </p>
        <div class="seo-stats">
          <div class="stat-item">
            <span class="stat-number">147%</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Average organic traffic increase</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-item">
            <span class="stat-number">3.2x</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Faster indexing</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-item">
            <span class="stat-number">92%</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Pass Core Web Vitals</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <a href="/#contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">Get SEO Audit</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="seo-problems">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Why Your Current SEO Isn't Working</h2>
      <div class="problems-grid">
        <div class="problem-card">
          <h3>Slow Core Web Vitals</h3>
          <p>Google's Page Experience update made speed a ranking factor. Your WordPress site can't compete with sub-second Astro load times.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="problem-card">
          <h3>Poor Technical Foundation</h3>
          <p>Bloated code, render-blocking resources, and poor mobile performance are killing your rankings before content even matters.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="problem-card">
          <h3>Missing Structured Data</h3>
          <p>Your competitors are getting rich snippets while your listings look plain. Schema markup is critical for modern SEO.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="problem-card">
          <h3>Indexation Issues</h3>
          <p>JavaScript-heavy sites struggle with crawlability. Search engines can't properly index your content if it's client-side rendered.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="astro-seo-advantage">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">The Astro SEO Advantage</h2>
      <div class="advantages-list">
        <div class="advantage-item">
          <div class="advantage-icon">üöÄ</div>
          <h3>Perfect Core Web Vitals</h3>
          <p>Static HTML loads instantly, giving you the speed advantage Google rewards with higher rankings.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="advantage-item">
          <div class="advantage-icon">üîç</div>
          <h3>Crawl-Friendly Architecture</h3>
          <p>Pre-rendered HTML is exactly what search engine bots love. No JavaScript execution required for indexing.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="advantage-item">
          <div class="advantage-icon">üìä</div>
          <h3>Built-in Schema Markup</h3>
          <p>We implement structured data directly in your Astro components, ensuring rich snippets appear in search results.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="advantage-item">
          <div class="advantage-icon">üì±</div>
          <h3>Mobile-First Optimization</h3>
          <p>With mobile-first indexing, your mobile performance directly impacts rankings. Astro delivers on mobile.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="our-seo-process">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Our SEO Optimization Process</h2>
      <div class="process-grid">
        <div class="process-item">
          <div class="process-number">1</div>
          <h3>Technical Audit</h3>
          <p>Complete analysis of Core Web Vitals, crawlability, indexation, and technical SEO issues.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="process-item">
          <div class="process-number">2</div>
          <h3>Schema Implementation</h3>
          <p>Add structured data for rich snippets: reviews, products, FAQs, and business information.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="process-item">
          <div class="process-number">3</div>
          <h3>Performance Optimization</h3>
          <p>Optimize images, implement lazy loading, and ensure perfect Core Web Vitals scores.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="process-item">
          <div class="process-number">4</div>
          <h3>Content Optimization</h3>
          <p>Optimize meta tags, headings, internal linking, and content structure for target keywords.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="seo-features">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">What's Included</h2>
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-category">
          <h3>Technical SEO</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Core Web Vitals optimization</li>
            <li>Mobile-first responsive design</li>
            <li>Site speed optimization</li>
            <li>XML sitemap generation</li>
            <li>Robots.txt optimization</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-category">
          <h3>On-Page SEO</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Meta titles and descriptions</li>
            <li>Header tag optimization</li>
            <li>Internal linking strategy</li>
            <li>Image alt text optimization</li>
            <li>URL structure improvement</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-category">
          <h3>Structured Data</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Organization schema</li>
            <li>Product schema (e-commerce)</li>
            <li>Review and rating markup</li>
            <li>FAQ schema implementation</li>
            <li>Local business schema</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-category">
          <h3>Analytics & Tracking</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Google Analytics 4 setup</li>
            <li>Search Console integration</li>
            <li>Core Web Vitals monitoring</li>
            <li>Conversion tracking</li>
            <li>Performance reporting</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="pricing-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">SEO Optimization Investment</h2>
      <div class="pricing-cards">
        <div class="price-card">
          <h3>SEO Audit</h3>
          <div class="price">$499</div>
          <p>Comprehensive technical SEO analysis with actionable recommendations</p>
        </div>
        <div class="price-card featured">
          <div class="popular-badge">Most Popular</div>
          <h3>Complete Optimization</h3>
          <div class="price">$2,500 - $4,500</div>
          <p>Full technical SEO implementation for Astro sites</p>
        </div>
        <div class="price-card">
          <h3>Ongoing SEO</h3>
          <div class="price">$1,200/mo</div>
          <p>Monthly SEO management and optimization</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Ready to Dominate Search Results?</h2>
      <p>Your competitors are getting the traffic you deserve. Let's fix that.</p>
      <a href="/#contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">Start SEO Optimization</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
.service-hero {
  padding: calc(80px + var(--space-16)) 0 var(--space-16);
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7c3aed 0%, #3730a3 100%);
  color: #ffffff;
  text-align: center;
}

.seo-stats {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
  gap: var(--space-6);
  margin: var(--space-8) 0;
}

.stat-item {
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  padding: var(--space-4);
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
}

.stat-number {
  display: block;
  font-size: var(--text-3xl);
  font-weight: 800;
  color: #ffd700;
}

/* Use similar styling patterns as other service pages */
.section-title {
  font-size: clamp(var(--text-2xl), 4vw, var(--text-4xl));
  font-weight: 700;
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  color: var(--color-primary);
}

.seo-problems, .astro-seo-advantage, .our-seo-process, .seo-features {
  padding: var(--space-20) 0;
}

.seo-problems {
  background: var(--color-white);
}

.problems-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
  gap: var(--space-6);
}

.problem-card {
  background: var(--color-light-gray);
  padding: var(--space-6);
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  border-left: 4px solid #ef4444;
}

.astro-seo-advantage {
  background: var(--color-light-gray);
}

.advantages-list {
  display: grid;
  gap: var(--space-6);
}

.advantage-item {
  display: flex;
  gap: var(--space-4);
  background: var(--color-white);
  padding: var(--space-6);
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
}

.advantage-icon {
  font-size: var(--text-3xl);
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

.our-seo-process {
  background: var(--color-white);
}

.process-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
  gap: var(--space-6);
}

.process-item {
  text-align: center;
  padding: var(--space-6);
}

.process-number {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  width: 60px;
  height: 60px;
  background: var(--color-accent);
  color: #ffffff;
  border-radius: 50%;
  font-size: var(--text-xl);
  font-weight: 800;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
}

.seo-features {
  background: var(--color-light-gray);
}

.features-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
  gap: var(--space-6);
}

.feature-category {
  background: var(--color-white);
  padding: var(--space-6);
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
}

.pricing-section {
  padding: var(--space-20) 0;
  background: var(--color-white);
}

.pricing-cards {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
  gap: var(--space-6);
}

.price-card {
  background: var(--color-light-gray);
  padding: var(--space-6);
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  text-align: center;
}

.price {
  font-size: var(--text-2xl);
  font-weight: 800;
  color: var(--color-accent);
  margin: var(--space-4) 0;
}

.cta-section {
  padding: var(--space-20) 0;
  background: #1a1a2e;
  color: #ffffff;
  text-align: center;
}

.cta-section h2 {
  margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  color: #ffffff;
}
</style>